title: English Bulldog hitches ride on a baby's stroller | Daily Mail Online
text: show ad When both babies are too tired to walk! Lazy Betty the English Bulldog hitches a ride on a toddler's stroller Betty the English Bulldog was on a walk in Scotland with her owner who was pushing a stroller Betty decided she'd had enough exercise for the day She jumped into the stroller's storage space and stared lovingly at owner Owner, seeing hopeless situation, resigned herself to pushing both babies along Published: 17:45 GMT, 20 February 2017 | Updated: 18:59 GMT, 20 February 2017 50 shares
